{"tid":1189812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣憂狂徒掟燃燒彈影響反送中遊行：相信北京最開心","createTime":"2019-06-07T03:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T10:22:33.000Z","uid":48093,"like":11,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3de72e23e27d186ef43c138439cecdced1162de0","tid":1189812,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190607/large/1559878698_8b74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190607%2Flarge%2F1559878698_8b74.jpg&h=3c620682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣發起的反送中遊行將於周日（9日）舉行，由維園遊行至政府總部，網上近期突然流傳指學生動源有意在遊行期間「突襲」，更聲稱學生已經準備好「燃燒彈」，而在傳出流言的同時，警察總部對開一輛衝鋒車周五（7日）被一名男子投擲燃燒彈，令遊行前夕出現更多陰謀論。民陣召集人岑子杰認為，目前難以去評論事件是否與遊行有關，但的確會令部份有意參加遊行人士卻步，強調民陣會盡力確保遊行人士的安全。<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰認為，或許有人認為是共產黨特意在敏感時候作出有關行為，但強調目前仍未找到疑兇，「任何解讀都係陰謀論」。不過他指客觀效果的確令需要安全的遊行參與者卻步，「相信北京最開心，因為少一個人少一份壓力」岑認為今次事件會令糾察壓力增加，但相信學生不會做出不智行為，因為如果證實是學生所為，「最開心一定係共產黨建制派」，而目前武力升級最大問題在於，無論如何升級也及不上政府，「佢哋有水炮車、音波槍、橡膠子彈、催淚彈」。今次事件除了擔心遊行人士安全外，亦擔心警方會以維持公眾安全為由，不斷截查遊行人士身份證，令他們在安全與遊行表達訴求之間，站在兩難位置。民陣當日約派出200名糾察維持秩序，之後亦會與糾察作溝通，確保如何令遊行更安全。"},{"pid":"63af2a7bd87c3c398a40732d56e939cada254cc2","tid":1189812,"uid":80814,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"擔咩鳩嘢心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做返自己要做嘅嘢<br />\n咪撚篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb899978bf8c3ba53c64e69c542402fd23c7dab","tid":1189812,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:54:45.000Z","msg":"民陣當日約派出200名<span style=\"color: red;\">糾察</span>維持秩序，之後亦會與<span style=\"color: red;\">糾察</span>作溝通，確保如何令遊行更安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eabe242fb545ca4b07081573290391ff3cbbf77","tid":1189812,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77e5d5797aea851f018544f7ba934f6528c5f2f8","tid":1189812,"uid":36178,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"岑子杰, 你講多就錯多<br />\njust keep ur damn month shut"},{"pid":"414245d2fb78c508d833760cbb8af17eaf1e6975","tid":1189812,"uid":73381,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"又黎共產黨最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28528230e3d74bbe6384958c305a1ecfd4e5aa5c","tid":1189812,"uid":148987,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:58:56.000Z","msg":"「激嬲中共」<br />\n「邊個衝邊個鬼」<br />\n席就割左<br />\n黎緊小心糾察隊篤灰"},{"pid":"8030a780bcd735c822adbf492db6bcbd69bba07f","tid":1189812,"uid":153614,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T03:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mAWZtuC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmAWZtuC.gif&h=5726d299&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de891cc491bafd0e44a8122a3495ebca0fcc0841","tid":1189812,"uid":130895,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:03:57.000Z","msg":"好鬼 <br />\n估一下<br />\n警方之後就會話捉到 個班犯<br />\n再話佢地係犯修例班人<br />\n利用傳煤 塑造 69例行 係 暴亂/動<br />\n<br />\n令有部分人見到咁 轉軑唔去"},{"pid":"7a4c68dc4f0074dc2cc387a4f15abc8e99fe2b82","tid":1189812,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:08:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"feabf2fba9831b00e24cc3494b9e13acbc0fcf59","tid":1189812,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"414245d2fb78c508d833760cbb8af17eaf1e6975","tid":1189812,"uid":7338